                        "name": "Entangling Tresses",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "A rusalka can have up to eight creatures grabbed within their tresses at a time."
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "Flowing Hair",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "The rusalka attempts an <a aonid=\"3\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Athletics</a> check and compares the result to each grabbed creature\u2019s Fortitude DC. The rusalka moves each creature they succeed against up to 10 feet and each creature they critically succeed against up to 20 feet. This movement must all be within reach of its tresses.",
                        "action": {
                            "type": "stat_block_section",
